of the otome game,

00:03:00.548 --> 00:03:03.417 position:24% line:83% align:start
"Regalia of Saints,
Demons, and Maidens."

00:03:03.551 --> 00:03:05.586 position:21% line:83% align:start
The main story of the
game surrounds Lilia,

00:03:05.720 --> 00:03:07.989 position:19% line:83% align:start
a Holy Sword Maiden and
her battle with the big, bad

00:03:08.122 --> 00:03:09.824 position:35% line:89% align:start
