Holy Sword Maiden.

00:06:13.741 --> 00:06:16.077 position:21% line:83% align:start
So, there's no reason
I can't handle this.

00:06:21.582 --> 00:06:22.850 position:38% line:83% align:start
[CLAUDE]
Allow me.

00:06:22.984 --> 00:06:24.285 position:35% line:83% align:start
Oh, thanks!
That would be ever so help--

00:06:24.451 --> 00:06:25.686 position:38% line:89% align:start
[screams]

00:06:34.929 --> 00:06:38.032 position:16% line:83% align:start
[gasps] What in the sexy,
sexy dark lord?

00:06:38.165 --> 00:06:40.268 position:21% line:83% align:start
This man is even more
gorgeous in real life than his

00:06:40.400 --> 00:06:42.136 position:27% line:89% align:start
character sprite!

00:06:42.270 --> 00:06:45.706 position:10% line:83% align:start
How dare he just stand there,
looking so beautiful?

00:06:48.776 --> 00:06:51.979 position:21% line:83% align:start
What business does a
human like you have with me?

00:06:52.113 --> 00:06:55.683 position:13% line:83% align:start
Am I to assume that you're
Lord Claude Jeanne Elmir?

00:06:55.816 --> 00:06:57.785 position:38% line:83% align:start
[CLAUDE]
That's correct.

00:06:57.919 --> 00:07:01.222 position:19% line:83% align:start
In that case, I've come
to make you an offer.

00:07:01.355 --> 00:07:03.423 position:27% line:89% align:start
I must ask you...

00:07:03.557 --> 00:07:05.593 position:24% line:83% align:start
Will you marry me,
pretty please?

00:07:10.264 --> 00:07:11.632 position:38% line:83% align:start
[CLAUDE]
Am I mistaken,

00:07:11.766 --> 00:07:14.101 position:24% line:83% align:start
or did a human just
propose to me?

00:07:29.116 --> 00:07:32.019 position:5% line:83% align:start
[AILEEN] Growing up, I lived an
ideal life as the youngest child

00:07:32.153 --> 00:07:33.521 position:35% line:89% align:start
of a duke.

00:07:33.654 --> 00:07:36.157 position:7% line:89% align:start
However, because I was a girl,

00:07:36.290 --> 00:07:40.194 position:13% line:83% align:start
and because I wasn't quite
as strong as my brothers,

00:07:40.328 --> 00:07:42.363 position:5% line:89% align:start
I could never keep up with them.

00:07:42.495 --> 00:07:44.298 position:13% line:89% align:start
No matter how hard I tried.

00:07:44.432 --> 00:07:47.668 position:19% line:83% align:start
For the longest time,
I felt I had no worth.

00:07:48.803 --> 00:07:50.404 position:21% line:89% align:start
Then, I turned eight.

00:07:50.538 --> 00:07:53.908 position:10% line:83% align:start
Prince CÃ©dric proposed to me,
and my world changed.

00:07:54.041 --> 00:07:56.110 position:21% line:83% align:start
It was the first time
anyone believed that I could

00:07:56.243 --> 00:07:57.645 position:21% line:89% align:start
accomplish something.

00:07:57.778 --> 00:07:59.447 position:21% line:83% align:start
The idea of becoming
empress consumed

00:07:59.580 --> 00:08:01.649 position:16% line:89% align:start
my every waking thought.

00:08:01.782 --> 00:08:04.685 position:19% line:83% align:start
I threw myself into my
studies so I could be a wise

00:08:04.819 --> 00:08:06.921 position:27% line:89% align:start
and strong ruler.

00:08:07.054 --> 00:08:08.189 position:33% line:89% align:start
Before long,

00:08:08.322 --> 00:08:09.957 position:16% line:83% align:start
I was called an "arrogant
heiress" who believed

00:08:10.091 --> 00:08:11.759 position:10% line:83% align:start
she was better than everyone
else simply for being

00:08:11.892 --> 00:08:14.729 position:21% line:89% align:start
the prince's fiancÃ©e.

00:08:14.862 --> 00:08:16.197 position:19% line:83% align:start
I wonder if there was
more I could have done

00:08:16.330 --> 00:08:19.800 position:16% line:83% align:start
to make myself likeable,
to seem vulnerable.

00:08:19.934 --> 00:08:21.736 position:24% line:83% align:start
Maybe things would
have been different.

00:08:22.837 --> 00:08:24.705 position:33% line:83% align:start
[BEELZEBUTH]
His lordship is not upset.

00:08:24.839 --> 00:08:28.142 position:16% line:83% align:start
The lightning strike was
the result of his surprise.

00:08:28.275 --> 00:08:32.646 position:16% line:83% align:start
[AILEEN] Does that mean
he wasn't angry with me?

00:08:33.447 --> 00:08:34.782 position:41% line:83% align:start
[KEITH]
He's right.

00:08:34.915 --> 00:08:37.018 position:21% line:83% align:start
I've seen you do much
worse over much less.

00:08:37.151 --> 00:08:39.754 position:16% line:83% align:start
That doesn't explain why
you treated her injuries.

00:08:39.887 --> 00:08:41.389 position:19% line:89% align:start
I don't need a reason.

00:08:41.522 --> 00:08:43.491 position:13% line:83% align:start
But you're certain that she
wishes to marry you, lord?

00:08:43.624 --> 00:08:44.625 position:38% line:83% align:start
[AILEEN]
I remember.

00:08:44.759 --> 00:08:46.660 position:10% line:89% align:start
He has two aides, doesn't he?

00:08:46.794 --> 00:08:48.562 position:27% line:89% align:start
Keith, the human.

00:08:48.696 --> 00:08:50.831 position:13% line:89% align:start
And Beelzebuth, the demon.

00:08:50.965 --> 00:08:52.800 position:16% line:89% align:start
Only until she wakes up.

00:08:52.933 --> 00:08:55.302 position:21% line:83% align:start
There's a chance she
was sent to me as a trap,

00:08:55.436 --> 00:08:56.737 position:19% line:89% align:start
or perhaps she's a spy.

00:08:56.871 --> 00:08:58.072 position:38% line:83% align:start
[AILEEN]
Who, me?

00:09:02.043 --> 00:09:06.047 position:33% line:83% align:start
I assure you.
I came here of my own free will.

00:09:06.180 --> 00:09:08.149 position:38% line:83% align:start
[AILEEN]
Claude Jeanne Elmir.

00:09:08.282 --> 00:09:09.784 position:19% line:89% align:start
CÃ©dric's half-brother.

00:09:11.118 --> 00:09:13.421 position:13% line:83% align:start
His demonic nature revealed
itself when he was only

00:09:13.554 --> 00:09:15.122 position:30% line:89% align:start
ten years old.

00:09:15.256 --> 00:09:17.691 position:7% line:83% align:start
That got the poor kid stripped
of his inheritance as heir.

00:09:17.825 --> 00:09:19.427 position:21% line:83% align:start
The humans and demons
agreed to a truce

00:09:19.560 --> 00:09:23.264 position:13% line:83% align:start
and he was brought here to
live in an abandoned castle.

00:09:23.397 --> 00:09:25.966 position:21% line:83% align:start
Should his hatred for
humanity ever awaken him,

00:09:26.100 --> 00:09:28.469 position:16% line:83% align:start
he'll transform into the
final boss that kills Aileen

00:09:28.602 --> 00:09:30.004 position:33% line:89% align:start
in the game.

00:09:30.137 --> 00:09:32.573 position:24% line:83% align:start
To avoid that fate,
there's but one thing to do!

00:09:32.706 --> 00:09:34.675 position:5% line:89% align:start
My only desire is to marry you!

00:09:34.809 --> 00:09:36.710 position:13% line:89% align:start
I know I'll make you happy!

00:09:38.479 --> 00:09:40.081 position:24% line:89% align:start
Remove her at once.

00:09:41.682 --> 00:09:43.884 position:13% line:83% align:start
Well, I would be delighted
to leave just as soon as you

00:09:44.018 --> 00:09:45.920 position:16% line:89% align:start
agree to our engagement!

00:09:46.053 --> 00:09:48.055 position:38% line:83% align:start
[CLAUDE]
But I've only just met you!

00:09:48.189 --> 00:09:52.927 position:24% line:83% align:start
So how could you...
I... I mean...

00:09:53.060 --> 00:09:56.263 position:24% line:83% align:start
Is it possible that
you're in love with me?

00:09:56.397 --> 00:09:57.932 position:41% line:89% align:start
Ah, no!

00:09:58.065 --> 00:10:01.168 position:5% line:83% align:start
[KEITH] Ah, excuse me, my lord,
could you dial back the tornado?

00:10:01.302 --> 00:10:03.204 position:27% line:83% align:start
You dare to make
such a request of me,

00:10:03.337 --> 00:10:05.773 position:24% line:83% align:start
mere moments after
CÃ©dric dissolved your--

00:10:09.910 --> 00:10:11.278 position:33% line:89% align:start
Listen to me.

00:10:11.412 --> 00:10:13.414 position:19% line:83% align:start
I am more than aware of
how this might appear.

00:10:13.548 --> 00:10:16.917 position:10% line:83% align:start
But do you expect me to spend
my days crying over what I lost?

00:10:17.051 --> 00:10:19.720 position:13% line:83% align:start
I refuse to waste another
second of my precious life

00:10:19.854 --> 00:10:21.556 position:24% line:89% align:start
thinking about him!

00:10:21.689 --> 00:10:24.758 position:7% line:83% align:start
And that's why you're courting
a demon lord instead?

00:10:26.994 --> 00:10:28.829 position:16% line:89% align:start
Court you? Why, my lord,

00:10:28.963 --> 00:10:30.364 position:19% line:83% align:start
if I was simply looking
to court you,

00:10:30.498 --> 00:10:31.966 position:27% line:89% align:start
I could easily--

00:10:36.370 --> 00:10:39.740 position:16% line:83% align:start
I hope you'll forgive me
for appearing so disheveled.

00:10:39.874 --> 00:10:41.942 position:13% line:89% align:start
I will return another time.

00:10:42.076 --> 00:10:43.878 position:38% line:83% align:start
[CLAUDE]
There is no need for that.

00:10:50.317 --> 00:10:53.087 position:19% line:83% align:start
Now you have no reason
to return at all.

00:10:53.220 --> 00:10:54.155 position:35% line:89% align:start
So go away.

00:10:54.288 --> 00:10:56.056 position:38% line:83% align:start
[AILEEN]
I'll treasure this forever!

00:10:56.190 --> 00:10:57.158 position:38% line:89% align:start
[squeals]

00:10:57.291 --> 00:11:00.661 position:24% line:83% align:start
I've always wanted
a magical dress!

00:11:00.794 --> 00:11:02.730 position:30% line:89% align:start
It's so lovely!

00:11:07.134 --> 00:11:09.203 position:38% line:83% align:start
[AILEEN]
Did you just cast another spell?

00:11:09.336 --> 00:11:11.338 position:27% line:89% align:start
[KEITH chuckles]

00:11:11.472 --> 00:11:13.374 position:38% line:83% align:start
[CLAUDE]
Be gone!

00:11:23.317 --> 00:11:25.753 position:24% line:83% align:start
Using magic to send
me back home...

00:11:26.954 --> 00:11:28.422 position:24% line:89% align:start
You win this time.

00:11:29.190 --> 00:11:30.724 position:16% line:83% align:start
[RUDOLPH] I'm glad to see
you're looking well,

00:11:30.858 --> 00:11:33.160 position:16% line:89% align:start
given the circumstances.

00:11:33.294 --> 00:11:36.531 position:27% line:83% align:start
It's a shame this
is out of our control.

00:11:36.665 --> 00:11:38.132 position:38% line:83% align:start
[AILEEN]
He's already given up!

00:11:38.265 --> 00:11:39.900 position:5% line:83% align:start
As the Emperor's prime minister,
I figured he'd at least

00:11:40.034 --> 00:11:42.937 position:30% line:89% align:start
try to help me!

00:11:43.070 --> 00:11:44.705 position:38% line:83% align:start
[RUDOLPH]
You've received an invitation.

00:11:44.838 --> 00:11:47.308 position:24% line:83% align:start
From Prince CÃ©dric
and the Lady Lilia.

00:11:50.945 --> 00:11:52.846 position:30% line:83% align:start
