announce their engagement.

00:11:55.449 --> 00:11:57.218 position:16% line:83% align:start
It seems they would like
you to sign the nullification

00:11:57.351 --> 00:12:00.655 position:27% line:83% align:start
of your previous
engagement at that time.

00:12:00.788 --> 00:12:02.223 position:38% line:83% align:start
[AILEEN]
Would they, now?

00:12:02.356 --> 00:12:04.925 position:19% line:83% align:start
He wants an even larger
audience for my rejection?

00:12:05.059 --> 00:12:06.994 position:24% line:89% align:start
It would appear so.

00:12:07.127 --> 00:12:09.430 position:21% line:83% align:start
Though Lady Lilia was
polite enough to include

00:12:09.564 --> 00:12:12.534 position:10% line:89% align:start
a letter of her own as well.

00:12:12.667 --> 00:12:14.902 position:38% line:83% align:start
[AILEEN]
Then I suppose I'll go.

00:12:15.035 --> 00:12:16.370 position:5% line:89% align:start
If they're looking for a fight,

00:12:16.504 --> 00:12:19.139 position:19% line:83% align:start
it would be my pleasure
to oblige them.

00:12:20.575 --> 00:12:21.942 position:21% line:89% align:start
No turning back now.

00:12:22.076 --> 00:12:24.478 position:24% line:83% align:start
I have to win over
Lord Claude no matter what!

00:12:28.115 --> 00:12:31.051 position:13% line:83% align:start
Wait, what? How have I been
going in circles all day?

00:12:31.185 --> 00:12:33.854 position:21% line:83% align:start
Don't tell me that's
how magical barriers work!

00:12:36.857 --> 00:12:39.226 position:38% line:83% align:start
Oh, dear!
It's such a shame!

00:12:39.360 --> 00:12:42.496 position:19% line:83% align:start
I guess I brought these
cookies with me for nothing!

00:12:45.600 --> 00:12:46.967 position:38% line:89% align:start
This too!

00:12:48.969 --> 00:12:51.573 position:16% line:83% align:start
Servants deserve the same
dignity as their master.

00:12:51.706 --> 00:12:53.374 position:19% line:83% align:start
So I have brought this
bow with me as a gift

00:12:53.508 --> 00:12:56.310 position:27% line:83% align:start
for whoever might
speak on my behalf.

00:12:56.443 --> 00:12:59.514 position:16% line:83% align:start
Think of it as the symbol
of the gatekeeper.

00:13:01.081 --> 00:13:03.817 position:19% line:83% align:start
[ALMOND] "Symbol of the
gatekeeper" you say?

00:13:05.486 --> 00:13:07.421 position:27% line:89% align:start
[caws] You there!

00:13:07.555 --> 00:13:10.525 position:24% line:83% align:start
The only one worthy
of that symbol is me!

00:13:14.629 --> 00:13:18.832 position:5% line:89% align:start
My, my! Don't you look handsome?

00:13:18.966 --> 00:13:20.769 position:16% line:83% align:start
Please, feel free to help
yourself to one of these

00:13:20.901 --> 00:13:22.202 position:38% line:89% align:start
as well.

00:13:24.138 --> 00:13:26.006 position:5% line:89% align:start
I always loved almonds! Delic--

00:13:29.009 --> 00:13:30.244 position:38% line:89% align:start
Oh, dear.

00:13:36.551 --> 00:13:38.352 position:27% line:89% align:start
What did you do?

00:13:38.485 --> 00:13:41.155 position:16% line:83% align:start
I had that cookie infused
with an anesthetic.

00:13:41.288 --> 00:13:44.224 position:24% line:83% align:start
What a fool you are
for trusting a human.

00:13:44.358 --> 00:13:46.093 position:13% line:89% align:start
Now face the consequences!

00:13:46.226 --> 00:13:48.763 position:30% line:83% align:start
Since when have
humans been this scary?

00:13:48.896 --> 00:13:51.231 position:16% line:83% align:start
Hear me now, Lord Claude.
Show yourself!

00:13:51.365 --> 00:13:53.000 position:7% line:89% align:start
If you refuse to meet with me,

00:13:53.133 --> 00:13:55.770 position:5% line:83% align:start
I'll strip your gatekeeper bald,
one feather at a time!

00:13:55.903 --> 00:13:58.105 position:24% line:89% align:start
Did she say bald?!

00:14:07.314 --> 00:14:09.350 position:27% line:83% align:start
Lovely to see you
again, Lord Claude!

00:14:09.483 --> 00:14:12.486 position:10% line:83% align:start
Would you care to revive your
servant before we proceed?

00:14:18.359 --> 00:14:19.293 position:38% line:89% align:start
Go away!

00:14:19.426 --> 00:14:21.028 position:27% line:83% align:start
If you ever come
back, I'll kill you!

00:14:21.161 --> 00:14:23.598 position:13% line:83% align:start
That was simply payback for
your rudeness yesterday!

00:14:23.732 --> 00:14:25.232 position:21% line:89% align:start
Consider us even now.

00:14:28.536 --> 00:14:30.739 position:24% line:83% align:start
Nope! I won't fall
for that again!

00:14:30.871 --> 00:14:32.206 position:21% line:89% align:start
It's safe, I promise.

00:14:32.339 --> 00:14:35.442 position:19% line:83% align:start
I only added anesthetic
to the almond ones.

00:14:42.851 --> 00:14:44.184 position:16% line:89% align:start
She's telling the truth.

00:14:47.020 --> 00:14:48.690 position:10% line:89% align:start
Delicious! I love chocolate!

00:14:48.823 --> 00:14:51.358 position:13% line:83% align:start
[AILEEN] What shall we do?
Perhaps we could head inside.

00:14:51.492 --> 00:14:53.628 position:27% line:83% align:start
Wait, did you add
something to that cookie?

00:14:53.762 --> 00:14:55.195 position:38% line:89% align:start
Why, yes.

00:14:55.329 --> 00:14:57.030 position:13% line:83% align:start
Nothing bad, just a little
something I hoped might

00:14:57.164 --> 00:14:58.932 position:13% line:89% align:start
change your mind about me.

00:14:59.066 --> 00:15:00.267 position:30% line:89% align:start
A love potion.

00:15:02.604 --> 00:15:07.074 position:30% line:89% align:start
[KEITH laughs]

00:15:07.207 --> 00:15:08.810 position:10% line:89% align:start
You're absolutely ridiculous.

00:15:08.942 --> 00:15:11.445 position:7% line:83% align:start
I just received word that I've
been invited to attend a ball

00:15:11.579 --> 00:15:12.881 position:21% line:89% align:start
two months from now.

00:15:13.013 --> 00:15:15.416 position:10% line:83% align:start
And I was hoping that I might
be able to persuade you

00:15:15.550 --> 00:15:16.684 position:33% line:89% align:start
to escort me.

00:15:16.818 --> 00:15:18.318 position:16% line:83% align:start
What does the love potion
have to do with that?

00:15:18.452 --> 00:15:20.287 position:21% line:83% align:start
After the outcome of
our previous meeting,

00:15:20.421 --> 00:15:22.757 position:16% line:83% align:start
I assumed that you would
turn me down without it.

00:15:22.891 --> 00:15:25.058 position:5% line:89% align:start
I was going for a fait accompli.

00:15:25.192 --> 00:15:27.494 position:21% line:83% align:start
[ALMOND] Demon Lord!
We've got a problem!

00:15:29.329 --> 00:15:30.497 position:21% line:89% align:start
Hello again, Almond!

00:15:30.632 --> 00:15:32.734 position:38% line:83% align:start
[ALMOND]
Don't call me that, it's stupid!

00:15:32.867 --> 00:15:33.934 position:38% line:83% align:start
[CLAUDE]
Ignore her.

00:15:34.067 --> 00:15:35.035 position:30% line:89% align:start
What happened?

00:15:35.169 --> 00:15:36.604 position:10% line:89% align:start
It's the fenrir cub, my lord!

00:15:36.738 --> 00:15:38.338 position:19% line:89% align:start
It's not in the forest!

00:15:40.675 --> 00:15:42.409 position:13% line:83% align:start
It appears to have escaped
from the second floor

00:15:42.544 --> 00:15:46.180 position:13% line:83% align:start
to the east and has already
made it past the barrier.

00:15:46.313 --> 00:15:48.415 position:16% line:83% align:start
Do you think it could be
headed for the school?

00:15:48.550 --> 00:15:52.821 position:21% line:83% align:start
What if the students
get their hands on it?

00:15:52.953 --> 00:15:54.388 position:16% line:89% align:start
I'll retrieve it at once.

00:15:54.522 --> 00:15:56.290 position:16% line:83% align:start
But if any humans were to
see you it would only serve

00:15:56.423 --> 00:15:59.026 position:30% line:83% align:start
to escalate the
situation even further.

00:15:59.159 --> 00:16:00.628 position:38% line:83% align:start
[AILEEN]
Allow me to help.

00:16:04.799 --> 00:16:06.634 position:27% line:83% align:start
I'm familiar with
the school's territory,

00:16:06.768 --> 00:16:08.837 position:21% line:83% align:start
and I should be able
to locate it quickly.

00:16:08.969 --> 00:16:11.138 position:27% line:83% align:start
It may be a cub,
but it's still a fenrir.

00:16:11.271 --> 00:16:13.474 position:16% line:83% align:start
It'll tear you to pieces
in an instant.

00:16:16.511 --> 00:16:18.947 position:24% line:83% align:start
If that's the case,
please allow me to take this.

00:16:19.079 --> 00:16:22.449 position:19% line:83% align:start
Your scent might have a
calming effect on the creature.

00:16:22.584 --> 00:16:25.787 position:10% line:83% align:start
Good thought, but what reason
do you have to aid me?

00:16:25.920 --> 00:16:28.455 position:21% line:83% align:start
I can't help but feel
sorry for the poor thing,

00:16:28.590 --> 00:16:31.526 position:10% line:83% align:start
but I'd be lying if I said I
wasn't hoping to have you

00:16:31.659 --> 00:16:32.560 position:24% line:89% align:start
in my debt as well.

00:16:32.694 --> 00:16:34.662 position:27% line:83% align:start
What do you mean,
"in your debt"?

00:16:34.796 --> 00:16:36.163 position:27% line:89% align:start
Well, just that!

00:16:36.296 --> 00:16:38.700 position:16% line:83% align:start
I do believe I can help,
so let me grant your wish.

00:16:40.300 --> 00:16:41.703 position:30% line:89% align:start
Don't fail me.

00:16:47.742 --> 00:16:49.009 position:38% line:83% align:start
[AILEEN]
"Don't fail me"?

00:16:49.142 --> 00:16:50.444 position:33% line:89% align:start
My goodness.

00:16:53.313 --> 00:16:55.783 position:16% line:83% align:start
It's rather nice to have
someone depend on you.

00:16:57.084 --> 00:17:01.556 position:7% line:83% align:start
Besides, if a child is missing,
you have to find them!

00:17:11.833 --> 00:17:15.235 position:13% line:89% align:start
[FENRIR growling, barking]

00:17:15.369 --> 00:17:17.805 position:7% line:83% align:start
[STUDENT A] Okay! I've got it!
Aim for the head!

00:17:17.939 --> 00:17:19.607 position:35% line:83% align:start
[STUDENT B]
Hold him down!

00:17:19.741 --> 00:17:21.009 position:38% line:89% align:start
[barking]

00:17:21.141 --> 00:17:22.810 position:10% line:83% align:start
Just do it, quick, while it's
still caught in the trap!

00:17:22.944 --> 00:17:24.512 position:10% line:83% align:start
[STUDENT B] You think this'll
get us promoted to the

00:17:24.646 --> 00:17:25.647 position:33% line:89% align:start
Holy Knights?

00:17:25.780 --> 00:17:27.882 position:38% line:83% align:start
[AILEEN]
Fancy yourselves demon slayers?

00:17:28.016 --> 00:17:30.117 position:13% line:83% align:start
Or have you all completely
forgotten the terms

00:17:30.250 --> 00:17:31.686 position:33% line:89% align:start
of the truce?

00:17:33.220 --> 00:17:34.722 position:33% line:83% align:start
[STUDENT B]
Lady Aileen!

00:17:34.856 --> 00:17:36.791 position:33% line:83% align:start
But I thought
you'd been expelled!

00:17:36.925 --> 00:17:39.126 position:38% line:89% align:start
[barking]

00:17:43.831 --> 00:17:47.200 position:19% line:83% align:start
It's nice to meet you.
My name is Aileen.

00:17:47.334 --> 00:17:49.003 position:24% line:83% align:start
Would you allow me
to take you back home?

00:17:49.136 --> 00:17:50.805 position:35% line:89% align:start
[growling]

00:17:56.243 --> 00:17:57.679 position:30% line:89% align:start
[AILEEN gasps]

00:18:02.182 --> 00:18:03.383 position:5% line:89% align:start
What do you think you're doing?

00:18:03.518 --> 00:18:05.352 position:35% line:83% align:start
[STUDENT B]
We can't let it get away!

00:18:06.754 --> 00:18:08.723 position:38% line:83% align:start
[AILEEN]
Stop that! You're hurting it!

00:18:08.856 --> 00:18:11.191 position:30% line:89% align:start
[STUDENTS yell]

00:18:18.498 --> 00:18:22.169 position:10% line:83% align:start
[AILEEN] The mother crossed
the barrier to find her cub!

00:18:22.302 --> 00:18:23.805 position:19% line:89% align:start
I beg you, don't howl!

00:18:23.938 --> 00:18:25.305 position:30% line:89% align:start
It's dangerous!

00:18:30.143 --> 00:18:33.213 position:30% line:89% align:start
[FENRIR barks]

00:18:34.749 --> 00:18:35.850 position:33% line:89% align:start
You're free!

00:18:52.332 --> 00:18:53.835 position:38% line:83% align:start
[CÃDRIC]
Aileen!

00:18:55.536 --> 00:18:57.105 position:38% line:83% align:start
[AILEEN]
Prince CÃ©dric.

00:18:57.705 --> 00:19:00.374 position:5% line:83% align:start
I was just informed that you had
summoned a savage demon

00:19:00.508 --> 00:19:03.011 position:24% line:83% align:start
onto school grounds
in order to attack Lilia.

00:19:03.143 --> 00:19:04.946 position:10% line:83% align:start
[AILEEN] And you were willing
to believe that I would do

00:19:05.079 --> 00:19:06.748 position:16% line:89% align:start
something so ridiculous?

00:19:06.881 --> 00:19:08.816 position:30% line:83% align:start
Who knows what
you're capable of.

00:19:08.950 --> 00:19:10.484 position:41% line:83% align:start
[LILIA]
Wait!

00:19:10.618 --> 00:19:13.320 position:5% line:83% align:start
I don't believe that Lady Aileen
would do something so awful!

00:19:13.453 --> 00:19:15.790 position:19% line:89% align:start
Please, Prince CÃ©dric!

00:19:15.923 --> 00:19:19.127 position:10% line:83% align:start
I'm willing to look past this
because Lilia asked me to.

00:19:19.259 --> 00:19:20.795 position:7% line:89% align:start
Leave before I change my mind.

00:19:20.928 --> 00:19:23.064 position:24% line:83% align:start
[LILIA] But look at
her hand! She's hurt!

00:19:23.196 --> 00:19:24.331 position:38% line:83% align:start
[CÃDRIC]
That's her fault.

00:19:24.464 --> 00:19:26.166 position:21% line:83% align:start
And she's overstayed
her welcome.

00:19:26.299 --> 00:19:27.401 position:27% line:89% align:start
Let's go, Marcus.

00:19:27.535 --> 00:19:29.403 position:38% line:83% align:start
[MARCUS]
Ha. How pathetic.

00:19:29.537 --> 00:19:31.639 position:13% line:83% align:start
[AILEEN] Hearing that from
him doesn't hurt anymore.

00:19:31.773 --> 00:19:34.408 position:21% line:83% align:start
He was over kindness
a long time ago.

00:19:44.251 --> 00:19:45.419 position:30% line:89% align:start
Why's he here?

00:19:45.553 --> 00:19:47.155 position:38% line:83% align:start
[MARCUS]
The demon lord!

00:19:47.287 --> 00:19:49.557 position:13% line:83% align:start
[LILIA] I thought he wasn't
supposed to leave the forest!

00:19:55.096 --> 00:19:56.329 position:24% line:89% align:start
Goodness, Brother.

00:19:56.463 --> 00:19:58.365 position:10% line:89% align:start
What brings you all this way?

00:19:59.534 --> 00:20:02.537 position:16% line:89% align:start
Aileen Lauren d'Autriche.

00:20:02.670 --> 00:20:03.838 position:38% line:89% align:start
Uh, huh?

00:20:07.875 --> 00:20:11.079 position:16% line:83% align:start
I owe you thanks for what
you have done tonight.

00:20:11.211 --> 00:20:14.048 position:10% line:83% align:start
You were willing to risk your
life to aid the fenrir cub

00:20:14.182 --> 00:20:16.718 position:27% line:83% align:start
without fear for
your own safety.

00:20:16.851 --> 00:20:18.886 position:16% line:83% align:start
You took the blame for a
crime you did not commit

00:20:19.020 --> 00:20:22.355 position:13% line:83% align:start
in order to prevent a war
between demons and humans.

00:20:25.093 --> 00:20:30.397 position:16% line:83% align:start
As the demon lord, please
accept my utmost thanks.

00:20:31.933 --> 00:20:34.334 position:38% line:83% align:start
[AILEEN]
He came here just to help me.

00:20:34.468 --> 00:20:37.839 position:5% line:89% align:start
To explain what really happened.

00:20:37.972 --> 00:20:40.340 position:21% line:83% align:start
But why in the world
would he do that?

00:20:40.474 --> 00:20:42.309 position:19% line:89% align:start
He has nothing to gain.

00:20:45.345 --> 00:20:47.849 position:27% line:83% align:start
May I escort you
back to your estate?

00:20:53.320 --> 00:20:55.623 position:27% line:83% align:start
Wait! How did you
make that appear?

00:20:55.757 --> 00:20:58.258 position:21% line:83% align:start
[CLAUDE] You'll find
I'm full of surprises.

00:21:16.544 --> 00:21:18.278 position:30% line:89% align:start
It's beautiful!

00:21:19.947 --> 00:21:21.682 position:16% line:83% align:start
[CLAUDE] You almost look
like an ordinary girl,

00:21:21.816 --> 00:21:23.184 position:30% line:83% align:start
gazing out the
window like that.

00:21:23.316 --> 00:21:24.652 position:19% line:89% align:start
That's extremely rude!

00:21:24.786 --> 00:21:27.155 position:19% line:83% align:start
I'm perfectly ordinary,
thank you very much.

00:21:27.287 --> 00:21:28.990 position:13% line:89% align:start
You're a unique individual.

00:21:29.123 --> 00:21:30.558 position:5% line:89% align:start
Though you've been through much.

00:21:30.691 --> 00:21:33.227 position:16% line:83% align:start
I've yet to see you shed
a tear or make an excuse.

00:21:33.360 --> 00:21:35.062 position:30% line:89% align:start
You're strong.

00:21:35.196 --> 00:21:39.567 position:5% line:83% align:start
But I still don't understand why
you would want to marry me.

00:21:39.700 --> 00:21:41.502 position:16% line:83% align:start
I'm not convinced you'd
believe me if I gave you

00:21:41.636 --> 00:21:43.004 position:21% line:89% align:start
the real reason why.

00:21:43.137 --> 00:21:45.606 position:30% line:83% align:start
I might be more
understanding than you think.

00:21:48.910 --> 00:21:50.645 position:19% line:83% align:start
If you're really sure,
then I'll tell you!

00:21:50.778 --> 00:21:52.847 position:7% line:83% align:start
This entire world and everyone
in it are actually part of

00:21:52.980 --> 00:21:55.716 position:19% line:83% align:start
an otome game I played
in my previous life!

00:21:55.850 --> 00:21:57.552 position:19% line:83% align:start
I'm one of the villain
characters, and if this doesn't

00:21:57.685 --> 00:22:00.154 position:21% line:83% align:start
go my way, you end up
turning into a giant dragon

00:22:00.288 --> 00:22:01.722 position:21% line:89% align:start
and then killing me!

00:22:04.324 --> 00:22:05.458 position:24% line:89% align:start
It's quite obvious.

00:22:05.593 --> 00:22:07.327 position:13% line:89% align:start
I see what's going on here.

00:22:08.930 --> 00:22:11.331 position:27% line:83% align:start
You enjoy making
a fool out of me!

00:22:11.464 --> 00:22:13.000 position:38% line:89% align:start
No, wait!

00:22:13.134 --> 00:22:14.635 position:35% line:89% align:start
Am I dying?

00:22:31.219 --> 00:22:32.887 position:38% line:83% align:start
[AILEEN]
A shooting star?

00:22:42.429 --> 00:22:44.265 position:13% line:89% align:start
How can you be so reckless?

00:22:44.397 --> 00:22:45.566 position:21% line:83% align:start
What were you trying
to do to me--

00:22:45.700 --> 00:22:48.102 position:27% line:83% align:start
I will accompany
you to the ball.

00:22:49.503 --> 00:22:51.505 position:27% line:83% align:start
After all, I have
a debt to repay.

00:22:51.639 --> 00:22:54.075 position:13% line:89% align:start
This is what you want, yes?

00:22:54.208 --> 00:22:56.443 position:13% line:89% align:start
Well, yes, of course it is.

00:22:56.577 --> 00:22:58.445 position:30% line:89% align:start
But then why...

00:22:58.579 --> 00:23:00.380 position:21% line:89% align:start
Why are you smiling?

00:23:03.251 --> 00:23:04.719 position:38% line:83% align:start
[CLAUDE]
I realized...

00:23:07.054 --> 00:23:10.024 position:27% line:83% align:start
I would very much
like to see you cry.

00:23:34.849 --> 00:23:38.219 position:16% line:83% align:start
[AILEEN] For some reason,
I have this feeling...

00:23:39.353 --> 00:23:43.991 position:5% line:83% align:start
...that my unfortunate end isn't
as certain as it used to be.

